  "texts": [
    "Errors created here can spread across the system and disturb clinical operations.",
    "Generally, the following factors can help a digital imaging department integrate image acquisition equipment (Andriole, 2006).",
    "• The simplicity of integrating the gadget into the clinical environment's established daily workflow routine.",
    "• High device fault tolerance and dependability.",
    "• User interface simplicity and intuitiveness."
  ]
